JustLapIt is a workout timer application that provides:
- Customizable interval timers
- Multiple workout modes (Time-Based, Multi-Phase, Distance-Based)
- Workout tracking and history
- Optional cloud sync for Premium subscribers
- Push notifications and workout reminders (Premium)

