## 8. Health, Safety & Medical Disclaimer

**⚠️ IMPORTANT: READ THIS SECTION CAREFULLY**

### 8.1 Not a Medical Device
JustLapIt is a general fitness timing tool. **IT IS NOT A MEDICAL DEVICE AND DOES NOT PROVIDE MEDICAL ADVICE.**

- The App is intended for general fitness and wellness purposes only
- Nothing in this App should be construed as medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment
- The App is not intended to replace professional medical advice or consultation

### 8.2 Fitness Data Accuracy
All fitness metrics provided by the App are **estimates only** and may be inaccurate:
- **Calorie calculations** are approximations based on general formulas and may not reflect your actual calorie expenditure
- **GPS tracking** is subject to device limitations, signal interference, and environmental factors
- **Pace and distance measurements** may vary from actual values
- **Workout statistics** should not be relied upon for medical or clinical purposes

### 8.3 Assumption of Risk
**BY USING THIS APP, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE AND AGREE THAT:**
- Physical exercise involves inherent risks, including but not limited to: physical injury, heart attack, stroke, dehydration, muscle strain, and in extreme cases, death
- You voluntarily assume all risks associated with using this App and performing any exercises or workouts
- You are solely responsible for your own health, safety, and wellbeing during any workout or physical activity

### 8.4 Your Responsibilities
**YOU ARE SOLELY RESPONSIBLE FOR:**
- Consulting a qualified healthcare provider before beginning any exercise program, especially if you have any medical conditions, injuries, or concerns
- Ensuring you are physically fit and healthy enough to engage in physical exercise
- Staying properly hydrated before, during, and after workouts
- Exercising in safe environments and conditions
- Warming up and cooling down appropriately
- Listening to your body and stopping immediately if you experience pain, dizziness, nausea, shortness of breath, chest pain, or any other discomfort
- Using appropriate safety equipment and attire
- Being aware of your surroundings when using GPS tracking features (traffic, terrain, weather, etc.)

### 8.5 No Liability for Injury
**TO THE FULLEST EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW:**
- Living Excellence Games shall NOT be held liable for any injury, death, damage, or loss of any kind arising from or related to your use of this App
- This includes, but is not limited to: physical injuries, accidents, health complications, property damage, or any other harm that may occur during, before, or after using the App
- You expressly waive any claims against Living Excellence Games for injuries or damages resulting from workouts, exercises, or any physical activity performed while using or as a result of using this App

### 8.6 Emergency Situations
- In case of medical emergency, contact emergency services immediately
- Do not rely on this App for emergency assistance
- The App does not have the capability to call for help or alert emergency services

**USE THE APP ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN RISK.**

